# Rui Seca's Portfolio  

## About  
- A personal portfolio showcasing my journey, projects, and skills.  
- Designed with a clean and modern interface, emphasizing usability and aesthetics.  

## Features  
- **Introduction**: Learn more about me, my background, and passions.  
- **Projects**:  
  - Explore my work, including GitHub repositories and live project links.  
  - Direct redirection for live website previews.  
- **Skills**: Highlighting the technologies, tools, and frameworks I excel at.  
- **Career Path Piano**:  
  - A unique and creative visualization of my career inspired by my love for playing the piano in real life.  
- **Contact**:  
  - Multiple ways to connect, including email and professional profiles.  

## Additional Features  
- **Dark/White Mode Toggle**:  
  - Customize your viewing experience with a sleek theme switcher.  

## Technologies Used  
- Built with modern web technologies for optimal performance and style.  

## How to Access  
- Visit the live portfolio [Webisite](https://portfolio-show-case.netlify.app/).

- Explore my GitHub repositories [Repo](https://github.com/RuiSeca/Portfolio/tree/master-piano).  

